{"tid":414282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"俄「食人魔夫妻」被捕 稱18年吃掉30人","createTime":"2017-09-26T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T15:21:20.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32adf3f928581f7bf848f64ace69d3a1f24f1e61","tid":414282,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vIrH2Fw4UwwcuNmTdAAEPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-09-26/c6864600-a263-11e7-a493-71e44ecb03da__2017092609481035730_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvIrH2Fw4UwwcuNmTdAAEPQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-09-26%2Fc6864600-a263-11e7-a493-71e44ecb03da__2017092609481035730_detail.jpg&h=0a330391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】天網恢恢，俄羅斯警方偶然下拘捕了一對「食人魔夫妻」，初步調查顯示，他們18年來至少吃掉了30人。警方在他們的家中起出了7袋冷凍屍塊，初步判定屍塊來自8名不同的死者，另外還有多個裝有殘肢的玻璃罐及19張人皮。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯媒體《Russia Today》報導，警方在本月11日接報指，俄羅斯南部的克拉斯諾達 (Krasnodar)一處軍校旁，出現裝有女性的殘肢的手提袋。一名工人又拾獲一部手機，內在許多人體屍塊的照片，警方根據線索追查到35歲男子 Dmitry Bakshaev 及其42歲妻子、護士 Natalia Baksheeva。兩人被捕後承認從1999年開始犯案，行兇手法主要用藥物迷暈受害人。<br />\n<br />\n而兩人最近一次犯案是在9月8日，他們在當地一處廢棄區域喝酒時，與死者發生衝突，後將她殺害和肢解，大部份殘肢被帶走，但仍有一小部份留在原地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84-%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%94%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%A8%B118%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%83%E6%8E%8930%E4%BA%BA-020000423.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%2584-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AD%2594%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A6%25BB-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%25A8%25B118%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2590%2583%25E6%258E%258930%25E4%25BA%25BA-020000423.html&d=rBfpHBYQ%2B%2FGRiKl7zPHeAU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=94194338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84-%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%94%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%A8%B118%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%83%E6%8E%8930%E4%BA%BA-020000423.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b36bd9e284cf288fd7c31f08cd496593f29b2cd","tid":414282,"uid":126293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"其實食人有冇問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f479c2582fc71f0a7c4f52500cd8c2865d9688a","tid":414282,"uid":8771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"喰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7bae5d3989d9127be2de352ec16354fbd17378","tid":414282,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"好食？"},{"pid":"8fc183924eff7e2013bd29f0a91e43a3b6776415","tid":414282,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"18年先食30人都唔餓死"},{"pid":"558e4a99f21cb9e6deeb2293b9552764d425770a","tid":414282,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"關係飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd373ac7de763a29314230a297b6a4ef0cc55e","tid":414282,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>18年先食30人都唔餓死</blockquote><br />\n你唔比人地食埋動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}